1
00:00:01,250 --> 00:00:12,340
Marcia met Howard Collins at church. Marcia
was thirty-five years old, Howard was forty-one.

2
00:00:12,340 --> 00:00:24,260
Howard lived with his mother in a small house
on the south side of the town. Marcia lived

3
00:00:24,260 --> 00:00:30,740
with her sister and father in an apartment,
three streets away.

4
00:00:30,740 --> 00:00:42,440
Marcia did not work. Her father, George Grant,
was ill and never left the apartment. He stayed

5
00:00:42,440 --> 00:00:53,149
in bed most of the time and always needed
somebody with him. So Marcia stayed at home

6
00:00:53,149 --> 00:01:03,240
with her father, and only went out when her
sister Karin was in the house.

7
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:14,520
The two sisters were very different. Marcia
was short with a small round face and short

8
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:29,570
black hair. Karin was ten years younger. She
was tall, had long brown hair, and good legs,

9
00:01:29,570 --> 00:01:38,640
and a suntan all through the summer. People
often said to Marcia, 'Your sister is very

10
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:49,080
beautiful.' There were always lots of men
ready to take Karin out to dinner or to the

11
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:54,310
cinema. But Marcia stayed at home.

12
00:01:54,310 --> 00:02:04,701
Karin worked in a shop in the town. When she
was at home, she liked to sit up on the roof

13
00:02:04,701 --> 00:02:08,259
garden of their apartment building.

14
00:02:08,259 --> 00:02:19,590
It was one Sunday in May when Marcia came
home with Howard the first time. She took

15
00:02:19,590 --> 00:02:32,700
him to see her father. George Grant was in
bed. He had grey hair and a grey face. Sometimes

16
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:40,860
he read a book, but mostly he just sat in
bed and watched television.

17
00:02:40,860 --> 00:02:54,180
'This is Howard, father,' Marcia said. 'He
works at the hospital, and we met at church.

18
00:02:54,180 --> 00:03:01,120
I told you about him last week. Do you remember?'

19
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:14,209
'No,' her father said. And he turned his face
away, back to his television. He was not interested

20
00:03:14,209 --> 00:03:19,470
in new people or his daughters' friends.

21
00:03:19,470 --> 00:03:30,170
Just then, Karin came into the room. She wore
a white bikini and white shoes. She smiled

22
00:03:30,170 --> 00:03:31,620
at Howard.

23
00:03:31,620 --> 00:03:42,849
'So you're Howard,' she said. 'My big sister
has got a boyfriend at last!'

24
00:03:42,849 --> 00:03:48,080
Howard's face went red and he looked down
