37
00:05:18,190 --> 00:05:29,900
Howard's face went red again. He gave a shy
little laugh. 'Oh, er... thank you,' he said.

38
00:05:29,900 --> 00:05:37,389
He tried not to look at Karin's long suntanned
legs, but it was not easy.

39
00:05:37,389 --> 00:05:49,759
'I come up here all the time when it's sunny,'
Karin said. She began to put suntan oil on

40
00:05:49,759 --> 00:05:53,389
