72
00:09:48,670 --> 00:09:50,600
Howard said nothing.

73
00:09:50,600 --> 00:10:02,810
It was a long, hot summer that year. Marcia
went to church every Sunday morning, and Karin

74
00:10:02,810 --> 00:10:11,580
stayed at home with their father. When it
was sunny - and it often was - Karin went

75
00:10:11,580 --> 00:10:14,640
up to her sunbed on the roof.

76
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:23,920
When Marcia went up to the roof garden, she
always sat under the umbrella. But Karin put

77
00:10:23,920 --> 00:10:29,279
on lots of suntan oil and sat in the sun in
her bikini.

78
00:10:29,279 --> 00:10:40,510
'The hot sun's not good for your body,' Marcia
said. Karin laughed. 'Howard likes my body.'

79
00:10:40,510 --> 00:10:45,240
'No, he doesn't!' Marcia said angrily.

80
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:55,750
'Oh, he does!' Karin said. 'He's very shy
with women, but he always looks at my body

81
00:10:55,750 --> 00:11:03,920
