134
00:18:07,530 --> 00:18:16,810
'I've got a bad head,' she told Karin. 'I
just phoned Howard and told him, and he's

135
00:18:16,810 --> 00:18:26,559
coming here after church as usual. I'm going
back to sleep for an hour or two.' And she

136
00:18:26,559 --> 00:18:30,220
went into her bedroom and shut the door.

137
00:18:30,220 --> 00:18:40,910
