opened her bottle of suntan oil.

144
00:19:21,650 --> 00:19:34,110
'Oh, there's not much here,' she said. 'I
must get some more.' She began to put some

145
00:19:34,110 --> 00:19:36,480
oil on her legs.

146
00:19:36,480 --> 00:19:46,460
